{"body": "Now that I have time to read the discussion I have to agree that we don't need add this complexity to Rails. It is to a very specific use case.\n\nAs @homakov said you always can use the `script` tag.\n\n```ruby\ntag(:script, src: 'http://foo.com/bar.js?baz=foo')\n```\n\nFor me this patch is adding a lot of complexity to a helper that I already think is too complex.\n\nIt can be only 100 lines but it also can increase the number of issues in the project.\n\nThat said I'm closing this one now.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/8397719", "created_at": "2012-09-08T20:43:34Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5187#issuecomment-8397719", "updated_at": "2012-09-08T20:43:34Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5187, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523ed88cbd354364b90136ef"}, "id": 8397719, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5187"}
